channel.title: How to change the ip in a 614 client
channel.description:
Hi, i can't find where to change the ip! i did go in bin and the only i saw were class files!
Picture: [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/jt75ly.png[/img]
After i changed the ip in launch and i compilled and run it, it says this: [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/2qnmp3n.png[/img]
Im using skaterscape 614 client
Thanks already!

item.title: How to change the ip in a 614 client
item.dc:creator: @camapple1 camapple1
item.description:
@camapple1 wrote:

First of all never change the ip in the bin also that is the cache error so all you need to do is change the cache path in cacheconstant.java and if it still doesnt work download the fixed error cache on mopar server downloads.

Hope i helped

Thanks.
